<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:white;"><span class="mw-headline" id="WikiProjects">WikiProjects</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #000000; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: white;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<p><b><a href="Wikipedia_WikiProject_Disability" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Disability">The Disability WikiProject</a></b> is a project that helps to assemble writers and editors interested in <a href="Disability" title="Disability">Disability</a> related articles. The aim of this project is to co-ordinate the improvement and creation of articles.</p>
